Follow the steps to run this application:

1. Download MAMP server on your PC from https://www.mamp.info/en/downloads/
2. After the download is complete, unzip the sxu171430_cs6360.zip into the htdocs folder present in the MAMP Application.
3. Open your command prompt or terminal and type mysql -u root -p and enter your password. Now, include the lib.sql file into your mysql database. This can be done by using the following command: 
source lib.sql;
4. Open MAMP and make sure that both the MySQL Server and the Apache Server are up and running.
5. After the servers are set up, go to http://localhost:8888/library.html. This is the homepage of the library management system. 
